{"tid":2127031,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"掃管芴又火燒旺地","createTime":"2020-07-27T06:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:37:11.000Z","uid":19552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1a71c888b254e3b0959c7bc4654b6e84be80f745","tid":2127031,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4935968/org/020a9b28581c79fc425110ffbaf6ccd2.jpg/pUA9BDKn7qvK_rfmdlawO136VCplwjco8zn-o9k5_qM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4935968%2Forg%2F020a9b28581c79fc425110ffbaf6ccd2.jpg%2FpUA9BDKn7qvK_rfmdlawO136VCplwjco8zn-o9k5_qM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=41722734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今午（27日）12時41分，屯門青山公路青山灣一建築地盤發生火警，火警至下午1時12分升為三級火，據悉該個地盤為鄰近黃金海岸的新盤帝御金灣地盤。消防接報後到場，現正動用兩條喉及兩隊煙帽隊灌救，約150人自行疏散到安全地方。現場消息指，涉事位置為新盤的第三座位置，現場濃煙衝天，一度傳出爆炸巨響，另外消防員利用地盤內的天秤吊起貨斗運載消防員，協助救起被困起火位置內的天秤工人。"},{"pid":"c8ff9f73f15181bafdf4613621b7d42c0c96803c","tid":2127031,"uid":19552,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3145537/org/bb7a5161cff35179344248ba9d086cf8.png/QTbGGKWbxORvnrS74OrtWg2rkI2b7FffpoWFeKaFhXg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3145537%2Forg%2Fbb7a5161cff35179344248ba9d086cf8.png%2FQTbGGKWbxORvnrS74OrtWg2rkI2b7FffpoWFeKaFhXg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2dcce6fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上回提要"},{"pid":"039a0ee38adcc5ac4420d20a975034bbaf736349","tid":2127031,"uid":171140,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ee3f5ad1584545d89b8427f5adc6967f0eb0897","tid":2127031,"uid":33868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"星期六日買完就即燒"},{"pid":"515f9fc07f0f388a3114b7ecb06005a5512509b9","tid":2127031,"uid":121697,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score"